using Plots
    function f(x)
      (-2 * x^2-4*x+3)/2
    end

    _x = range(-10, 10, length=100)

    plot(_x,f.(_x),label="f(x)=(-2 * x^2-4*x+3)/2")
    plot!(legend=:outerbottom, legendcolumns=1)
